<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，蚯蚓小组骑着自行车来到老教堂路的尽头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂迷路了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们走这条路，还是那条路？”她问道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要一个GPS！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但卢克认识路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他领着他们骑过一座旧桥，沿着一条泥土路走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们快到了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几分钟后，他们在一座老房子前停下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是这儿了。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>房子看上去没人住。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好可怕啊。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没人住在这里。”艾米丽说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们回家吧。”阿杰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘘，听。”艾米丽说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人在唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们下了自行车，顺着声音走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一位老妇人正在晾衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她边干活边唱着歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把最后一件衣服晾到绳子上，拿起篮子转过身来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们是谁？”她厉声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她看起来不好相处。”凯蒂想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是蚯蚓小组！”阿杰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米丽碰了一下她弟弟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是艾米丽。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卢克。”“阿杰。”“凯蒂。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们在这里干什么？我从来没有访客。”老妇人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在寻宝。”凯蒂回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老妇人看起来疑心重重。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们在这儿找什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您！”阿杰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“柳树溪最老的人。”艾米丽说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您是梅•亨德森奶奶，对吧？”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您弟弟给我们画了一张地图，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以我们找到了您。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我弟弟是个爱管闲事的人。”亨德森奶奶说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他有一辆T型福特！”阿杰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亨德森奶奶终于笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，是的。我听说过关于它的一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我弟弟说他很快会带我去兜风。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亨德森奶奶抬头看了看后门廊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你们不介意的话，我想坐下来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当大家都找好自己的位置后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克说：“您弟弟说他的T型车是柳树溪的第一辆车。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那可能是真的。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伦道夫•帕特森买T型车的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我还是个小学生，但大家都不喜欢那辆车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那辆车在路上飞驰时，到处都是灰尘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们不能呼吸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像我爸爸那样的农民们，说灰尘损害了庄稼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在洗衣服的日子，女人们就得把晾衣绳上的所有东西都收起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们不得不把洗好的衣服重新洗一遍。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您弟弟要开他的T型车参加柳树溪生日游行。”卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“柳树溪已经有150年的历史了。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！时间过得真快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当柳树溪50周年的时候，我还只是一个小女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它一百周年的时候，我的头发是灰色的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亨德森奶奶笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但现在，这个村子已经150周年了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。我们要参加游行。”艾米丽说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您也可以参加！”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不，我再也不进城了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亨德森奶奶摇着头说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，城里太吵了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您可以坐T型车！”阿杰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要走了。”艾米丽说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我得考虑一下。”亨德森奶奶说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奶奶，您能给我们的寻宝购物袋写张便条吗？”凯蒂问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亨德森奶奶笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当我还是个小女孩儿的时候，我做过很多次寻宝游戏。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她高兴地写了一张便条。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面写着：我叫梅•亨德森。我103岁了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚯蚓小组骑上了自行车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望在游行中见到您！”他们大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，朝马路骑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，可芙老师带领孩子们沿着柳树溪徒步旅行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给他们看了乌龟蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给他们看了一只在阳光下睡觉的蜥蜴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们采了野花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>347653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂在想着亨德森奶奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>347654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>352160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她八岁的时候沿着小溪散过步吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>352161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那时候，小溪是什么样子的呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>359679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，艾米丽抓住了凯蒂的胳膊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>359680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你听到了吗？”她低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>362626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>367366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙卷风小组今天要去养老院找最年长的人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>367367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>374877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈！”凯蒂说，“他们在那里永远找不到她！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>